{"tid":2442062,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"接種中心請長者食閉門羹 47歲男打科興後頭暈送院","createTime":"2021-03-11T06:31:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T06:52:45.000Z","uid":239336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"30a0cde830d2a2009f7ede524316c045b420bbcf","tid":2442062,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:31:35.000Z","msg":"本港市民接種科興疫苗後死亡個案，增至第三宗，其中涉及兩宗個案的官涌體育館疫苗接種中心，今日繼續有市民到場接種科興疫苗，有長者昨晚徹夜未眠，今早清晨出門到官涌接種疫苗，可是被中心職員查詢身體 狀況時，臨場被請食閉門羹，建議先諮詢醫生意見，令他大感失望。<br />\n<br />\n今早大約10時40分，有救護車到達官涌體育館疫苗接種中心，一名中名男子由擔架床送上救護車往伊利沙伯醫院，但未知是否已經完成疫苗接種，該男子全程清醒並使用手提電話，未有回應記者提問。目前三宗接種科興疫苗後出現死亡案例中，其中兩宗死者，都是在官涌接種疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n官涌疫苗接種中心發言人回覆本報查詢時表示，證實一名47歲男士上午9時48分於官涌接種中心注射科興疫苗，在休息區觀察期間感頭暈。醫護人員遂召喚救護車把該名男士送院。據悉該名男士沒有長期病患，但曾有「暈針」紀錄，送院前清醒，一切維生指數正常<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-QsPo393ucw7Q-_fY_jDthoUYyc=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MC6QSURMGFDUVHVIXOJZJ3OF6Q.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-QsPo393ucw7Q-_fY_jDthoUYyc%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMC6QSURMGFDUVHVIXOJZJ3OF6Q.JPG&h=7742bdcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n長者徐先生今早約9時便到達官涌體育館疫苗接種中心，誰知臨場被請食閉門羹，他表示中心內職員在接種前曾問他身體狀況，徐先生指會有抽筋情況，職員遂建議他先諮詢醫生是否適合接種，令徐先生失望而回，「反正都要死，只是遲或早，有甚麼需要擔心。」<br />\n<br />\n徐先生又指自己家住藍田，要先轉乘3轉車才到達現場，加上一直擔心熟睡聽不到鬧鐘聲，昨晚徹夜失眠，認為是浪費時間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/t-DsB5n7TA7gIhzZNBNcuWjjqyg=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IDHQEW536RBE3KHDRVDNF3LLXY.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ft-DsB5n7TA7gIhzZNBNcuWjjqyg%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIDHQEW536RBE3KHDRVDNF3LLXY.JPG&h=712761d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外今早市民歐小姐陪同六十多歲母親到官涌接種科興疫苗，母親有血壓高情況，但之前未有諮詢家庭醫生。她表示雖然自己對科興信心僅「一半半」，但由於是家人替母預約，也就陪同母親到來，「係家姐幫媽咪預約，覺得佢應該先接種，因為佢年紀較大，所以為佢預約。」<br />\n<br />\n衞生署將於數日內發出指引，清晰表列不適合接種武肺疫苗的情況，供私家醫生及市民參考。市民馮先生認為難以評論指引是否來得太遲，「大家有心找出原因，任何事也有正反兩面，做始終比不做好。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lYaicydKDV7NXCjII6mDHXb2-_Y=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SVAYXPF5JJBODEQ244Z3SUK6MI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlYaicydKDV7NXCjII6mDHXb2-_Y%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSVAYXPF5JJBODEQ244Z3SUK6MI.JPG&h=c73e64e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對於有多個市民接種疫苗後感不適需要送院，甚至出現3宗死亡個案，馮先生亦剛完成接種科興疫苗，自言沒有任何不適感覺，出現不適情況認為只屬個別例子，「你睇電視新聞，其實外國更嚴重，韓國仲厲害，所以電視新聞比較偏頗，只報道負面事情，一日有幾多人接種，嗰啲人感覺如何，沒有提及。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fRfcsOTkApTteP-vmdDVhMcdcC4=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OH5YWML2SZANFK42J47DHD47YE.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfRfcsOTkApTteP-vmdDVhMcdcC4%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOH5YWML2SZANFK42J47DHD47YE.JPG&h=a027339c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市民鐘先生認為應該早些公佈相關指引，「現在資訊發達，各人都有權利選擇係咪接種，我覺得早啲公佈較好。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，指引包括有長期有吸煙習慣，運動時有胸口痛或氣促，自知或懷疑患冠心病，則不宜接種疫苗。指引亦會清楚界定長期病患者不宜接種疫苗的指標，包括血壓長期達160／100以上，血糖HbA1C數值長期達10以上，或有甲狀腺問題，而以上病情未能透過藥物控制，均不適合或須延遲接種疫苗，直至成功控制病情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210311/5KYRQGGGCZB3HPB52QVCFAR7HY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210311%2F5KYRQGGGCZB3HPB52QVCFAR7HY%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=18185d9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210311%2F5KYRQGGGCZB3HPB52QVCFAR7HY%2F&h=8b351a5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210311/5KYRQGGGCZB3HPB52QVCFAR7HY/</a>"},{"pid":"3ad9462fc5ce41bca7232de6bc1b3e43ceca7f10","tid":2442062,"uid":126590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:36:35.000Z","msg":"即係所有食煙嘅人都唔洗打疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁又買幾百萬支疫苗？<br />\n特首同衛生署發緊夢？？"},{"pid":"7a45b8c9968e11771905b52fa10fc4d8ce667833","tid":2442062,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:38:04.000Z","msg":"個髮型幾型仔"},{"pid":"6bb1f3ae737c42b043d3eebfc55abd8a8ac6a581","tid":2442062,"uid":22422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:41:21.000Z","msg":"歐小姐兩姊妹咁撚孝順？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019aa44c72fbba3f0e7f32d4dcffd94bf2166c24","tid":2442062,"uid":71694,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/frLDyoy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfrLDyoy.gif&h=fbbac240&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"689076794f65ffdf988e6b3ae275c47926f95137","tid":2442062,"uid":9281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:43:49.000Z","msg":"個個樣都甩皮甩骨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17e8ab60b70ccb19ecfabe3dc33d144ab9b0ae4","tid":2442062,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T06:52:45.000Z","msg":"聽過幾個唔同嘅藍絲講<br />\n有長期病患，糖尿，高血壓嗰啲去問醫生<br />\n啲醫生都係話ok叫佢哋去打<br />\n唔知以為啲醫生要跑數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}